flowchart LR
    Producers[Event Producers\nApps, sensors, microservices] --> Platform[Streaming Platform\nKafka / Kinesis topics]
    Platform --> Engine[Stream Processing Engine\nFlink, Spark Streaming, Kafka Streams]
    Engine --> Stateless[Stateless Transforms\nFilter, project, type coerce]
    Stateless --> Windowed[Windowed Aggregations\nTumbling, sliding, session windows]
    Windowed --> StateStore[State Store\nRocksDB or managed state backend]
    Engine --> DeadLetter[Dead-Letter Topic\nFailed record capture]
    Windowed --> Sinks[Output Sinks]
    Sinks --> TSDB[Time-Series DB\nInfluxDB, Prometheus]
    Sinks --> KVStore[Key-Value Store\nRedis feature cache]
    Sinks --> ObjectStore[Object Store\nParquet for batch jobs]
    TSDB --> Dashboard[Operational Dashboard]
    KVStore --> APILayer[Feature Serving API]
